${H1}STAGE 2 — GATE TASK${RST}

Inside the practice prompt, do these (in any order):

  1. make a folder called ${DIR}practice${RST} (inside this stage's folder)
  2. cd into it
  3. confirm you're inside it with ${CMD}pwd${RST}

